        name: "1b", d_model: 1024, n_layer: 24, n_head: 16, n_kv_head: 4,
        block_size: 512, consciousness_dim: 128, atoms: 32, cells_per_atom: 8,
        batch_size: 32, lr: 0.00015, label: "Scale-3 (1B)"
    }
}

// Scale-3.5 (1.5B) — matches training/clm_1b_config.json (d=2048) and the
// successful r3f run from train_clm_1b.py. scale_1b above is only ~500M
// (d=1024); scale_1_5b is the true 1B+ byte-level scale and the direct
// .hexa port target for train_clm_1b.py. SwiGLU ff=8192 (3× factor) gives
// ~1.51B params per clm_1b_config.json param_count_estimate. Atom config
// copied from scale_1b so the consciousness controller stays compatible.
fn scale_1_5b() -> ScaleConfig {
    ScaleConfig {
        name: "1_5b", d_model: 2048, n_layer: 24, n_head: 16, n_kv_head: 8,
        block_size: 512, consciousness_dim: 128, atoms: 32, cells_per_atom: 8,
        batch_size: 8, lr: 0.0003, label: "Scale-3.5 (1.5B)"
